---
title: Beef Meatball & Daikon Noodle Curry with Coconut Sauce & Asian Greens
description: Introducing the ultimate solution to the classic dilemma; when you can’t decide between two superstar dishes.
Meatballs or curry, we say let’s have both! The creamy curry sauce will soak into the meatballs and the daikon
noodles do nicely to add a little extra texture and tastiness. You won’t ever have to compromise again.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*

